# Fluff Date: 2026-03-18 15:07:44
<overview>
<p>Clan motorized squads mount a squad-strength element on light vehicles for fast patrol and screening operations. These small, mobile formations extend garrison coverage along road networks and perimeter zones where a full motorized Point would be excessive. Their speed and low logistics footprint make them useful as early-warning elements and rapid checkpoint reinforcements across Clan occupation zones.</p>
</overview>

